      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey my left eye is super red and it's kinda hurting, plus there's like this yellowish stuff coming out of it when i wake up. i probably just have really dry eyes from being on my laptop all day for work. do u think i should just grab some over the counter lubricating drops at the pharmacy or is it something else?",
